<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们现在遇上了很大的麻烦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只巨大而生气的慈母龙妈妈正准备攻击他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么办法能出去吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们没办法从窝里爬出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个洞太深了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也没有地方躲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>恐龙很快就会找到他们的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！太阳要落山了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“分散恐龙的注意力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳就要落山了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊喊了回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他有了一个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它带走了兰姆但却没有伤害他。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许它以为兰姆是它的孩子。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这无所谓啦。”潘瑟叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须从这儿出去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟紧紧抓住了兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>恐龙发出了一声高喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它更生气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘瑟！我们把宝宝传来传去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟没听明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要孩子在谁手里，那只恐龙就不会伤害谁。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他解释说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟将兰姆递给了鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比迅速地将孩子递给了简。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简又将他交给了赛伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊最后把兰姆又递给了潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们就一直这样将兰姆传来传去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆咯咯笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他以为他们在玩儿游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>恐龙停下来看着孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它的小眼睛一直紧盯着兰姆，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但它看上去有点儿困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点，太阳！”赛伊祈祷着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳就要开始落山了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>恐龙终于不耐烦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它挥动着自己强壮的尾巴朝它的窝冲过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>越来越近了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都可以看到它尖尖的牙齿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们吓得瑟瑟发抖，紧紧地搂在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们意识到周围的一切都变得安静了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们睁开了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它不见了！”鲍比叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们终于安全了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们不再被巨大的生物包围着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们安全了！”简尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们开心得跳个不停。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟擦去眼泪抱起了兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>重新回到正常世界的感觉真是太棒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们最好回家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊抬头看着即将变黑的天空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨可能担心了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们回家的时候，玛莎阿姨刚好回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你过得愉快吗？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，谢谢你们。”她回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们今天过得怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看看彼此，都咧着嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好！”赛伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只恐龙抓走了兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，我们不得不去营救他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她并不相信赛伊说的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的想象力很棒。”她轻轻一笑，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在去吃晚饭吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，孩子们很早就醒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为玛莎阿姨还在睡觉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们就在走廊上坐下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天轮到谁许愿了？”简激动地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不觉得我们应该停止了吗？”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“停止什么？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“停止许愿。”潘瑟回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“许愿已经不再有意思了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的孩子思考着这个问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个主意。”赛伊最后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们每个人可以再许一个愿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，我们就保证不再许愿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了潘瑟以外的每个人都同意说这是个好主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我们现在就应该停止了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她争论说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不公平。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊已经许过两个愿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，这不公平！”简抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，潘瑟让步了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>89</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们快速地吃过早饭后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>90</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就朝休伊的那口井走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>91</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>339506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊把休伊拉了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>92</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345388</EndMilliseconds>
