  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>93</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊挤挤眼问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>94</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>347729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们度过了很棒的一天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>95</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊依旧嘴硬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>96</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊做了个鬼脸学他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>97</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>356648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，轮到你了。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>98</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>360274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比想了又想。</Text>
